{"tid":1135424,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中大民調：特首三司評分齊跌　近四成市民不信任中央政府","createTime":"2019-05-02T09:53:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-02T14:10:26.000Z","uid":241764,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c1b1a02702b4482e437dfc5cfa268623e92cc571","tid":1135424,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T09:53:20.000Z","msg":"中大亞太研究所發表4月民調，當中市民對於政府表現的滿意度，特首、三名司長表現評分，以至對中央政府和特區政府的信任度，與3月比較均下跌。<br />\n<br />\n政府滿意度方面，26.6%受訪市民表示滿意港府表現，較3月低2.3個百分點；表示不滿意的有37.1%，較3月高3個百分點；而政府信任度方面，26.7%受訪市民表示信任港府，較3月低2.9個百分點；表示不信任的則有28.3%，較3月高1.3個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n就特首林鄭月娥評分，受訪市民對特首整體表現平均評分為51分，較3月評分下跌2分，其中年齡為30歲或以下，及教育程度為大專或以上的受訪市民，給予評分相對較低。<br />\n<br />\n三名司長方面，政務司長張建宗評分為47.7分，較3月下跌1.7分；財政司長陳茂波評分為39.9分，較3月下跌0.4分；律政司長鄭若驊評分為36.5分，較3月下跌1.6分。<br />\n<br />\n另外，22%的受訪市民表示信任北京中央政府，較3月低1.6個百分點；表示不信任的有39.5%，較3月高1.9個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n若將最新4月民望調查指標與2018年4月比較，除對中央政府的信任度，其餘指標均低於去年同期，且跌幅顯著。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190502/s00001/1556786367641/%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E6%B0%91%E8%AA%BF-%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E4%B8%89%E5%8F%B8%E8%A9%95%E5%88%86%E9%BD%8A%E8%B7%8C-%E8%BF%91%E5%9B%9B%E6%88%90%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%8D%E4%BF%A1%E4%BB%BB%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190502%2Fs00001%2F1556786367641%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%25AA%25BF-%25E7%2589%25B9%25E9%25A6%2596%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%258F%25B8%25E8%25A9%2595%25E5%2588%2586%25E9%25BD%258A%25E8%25B7%258C-%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%259B%259B%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%258D%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25AE%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C&d=5W7Dp6DGRi9eT2AMHrnJu6hYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=5d6029de\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190502%2Fs00001%2F1556786367641%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%25AA%25BF-%25E7%2589%25B9%25E9%25A6%2596%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%258F%25B8%25E8%25A9%2595%25E5%2588%2586%25E9%25BD%258A%25E8%25B7%258C-%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%259B%259B%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%258D%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25AE%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C&h=24639785\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190502/s00001/1556786367641/%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E6%B0%91%E8%AA%BF-%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E4%B8%89%E5%8F%B8%E8%A9%95%E5%88%86%E9%BD%8A%E8%B7%8C-%E8%BF%91%E5%9B%9B%E6%88%90%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%8D%E4%BF%A1%E4%BB%BB%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C</a>"},{"pid":"639e58ba3ce128ae1f25cb22a7d81cbc392e2142","tid":1135424,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T09:54:30.000Z","msg":"40%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"550b19311575f8b0cbd286b0664e124cd011cc76","tid":1135424,"uid":15830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T10:03:05.000Z","msg":"得4成<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca401cbfd247d407de3c2b740195c489a71b42a5","tid":1135424,"uid":132189,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T13:00:05.000Z","msg":"6成有幾多係新移民同00後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a73073246793e2841b9966a6fcdde9c9baef0b5f","tid":1135424,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T13:27:06.000Z","msg":"4成算少啦"},{"pid":"ecca7862b1abff853c183a5988fca3e58fdc089f","tid":1135424,"uid":87780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T14:03:20.000Z","msg":"事實證明次次講唔關我事嫁啲港豬就會覺得真係唔關佢事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77eac6d77a7db28b398837937783c012e5818f1e","tid":1135424,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T14:10:26.0